These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, aconite
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Flower   | aconite | tulip | rose |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Sport   | climbing | volleyball | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, zombie, action
1. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | zombie | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, train, car
1. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Transport   | jet-ski | car | train |

