.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, montecristo, bolivar
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Cigar   | montecristo | bolivar | prince |

 